# Days on Market Predictor for Vehicle Sales Optimization

## Project Overview
This project aims to predict the number of days a vehicle will remain on the market before being sold. The solution involves data cleaning, feature engineering, and training two regression models—Ridge Regression and Linear Regression—to generate predictions. The project is structured following best practices in machine learning development, including modular code, version control, configuration management, and comprehensive documentation.

